{"ja441:0.1":"Jataka ","ja441:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","ja441:0.3":"Catudvaravagga ","ja441:0.4":"3. Catuposathiyajataka ","ja441:1.1":"“Yo kopaneyye na karoti kopam, ","ja441:1.2":"Na kujjhati sappuriso kadaci; ","ja441:1.3":"Kuddhopi so navikaroti kopam, ","ja441:1.4":"Tam ve naram samanamahu loke”. ","ja441:2.1":"“Unudaro yo sahate jighaccham, ","ja441:2.2":"Danto tapassi mitapanabhojano; ","ja441:2.3":"Aharahetu na karoti papam, ","ja441:2.4":"Tam ve naram samanamahu loke”. ","ja441:3.1":"“Khiddam ratim vippajahitvana sabbam, ","ja441:3.2":"Na calikam bhasasi kinci loke; ","ja441:3.3":"Vibhusatthana virato methunasma, ","ja441:3.4":"Tam ve naram samanamahu loke”. ","ja441:4.1":"“Pariggaham lobhadhammanca sabbam, ","ja441:4.2":"Yo ve parinnaya pariccajeti; ","ja441:4.3":"Dantam thitattam amamam nirasam, ","ja441:4.4":"Tam ve naram samanamahu loke”. ","ja441:5.1":"“Pucchama kattaramanomapannam, ","ja441:5.2":"Kathasu no viggaho atthi jato; ","ja441:5.3":"Chindajja kankham vicikicchitani, ","ja441:5.4":"Tadajja kankham vitaremu sabbe”. ","ja441:6.1":"“Ye pandita atthadasa bhavanti, ","ja441:6.2":"Bhasanti te yoniso tattha kale; ","ja441:6.3":"Katham nu kathanam abhasitanam, ","ja441:6.4":"Attham nayeyyum kusala janinda. ","ja441:7.1":"Katham have bhasati nagaraja, ","ja441:7.2":"Garulo pana venateyyo kimaha; ","ja441:7.3":"Gandhabbaraja pana kim vadesi, ","ja441:7.4":"Katham pana kurunam rajasettho”. ","ja441:8.1":"“Khantim have bhasati nagaraja, ","ja441:8.2":"Appaharam garulo venateyyo; ","ja441:8.3":"Gandhabbaraja rativippahanam, ","ja441:8.4":"Akincanam kurunam rajasettho”. ","ja441:9.1":"“Sabbani etani subhasitani, ","ja441:9.2":"Na hettha dubbhasitamatthi kinci; ","ja441:9.3":"Yasminca etani patitthitani, ","ja441:9.4":"Arava nabhya susamohitani; ","ja441:9.5":"Catubbhi dhammehi samangibhutam, ","ja441:9.6":"Tam ve naram samanamahu loke”. ","ja441:10.1":"“Tuvanhi settho tvamanuttarosi, ","ja441:10.2":"Tvam dhammagu dhammavidu sumedho; ","ja441:10.3":"Pannaya panham samadhiggahetva, ","ja441:10.4":"Acchecchi dhiro vicikicchitani; ","ja441:10.5":"Acchecchi kankham vicikicchitani, ","ja441:10.6":"Cundo yatha nagadantam kharena. ","ja441:11.1":"Niluppalabham vimalam anaggham, ","ja441:11.2":"Vattham idam dhumasamanavannam; ","ja441:11.3":"Panhassa veyyakaranena tuttho, ","ja441:11.4":"Dadami te dhammapujaya dhira. ","ja441:12.1":"Suvannamalam satapattaphullitam, ","ja441:12.2":"Sakesaram ratnasahassamanditam; ","ja441:12.3":"Panhassa veyyakaranena tuttho, ","ja441:12.4":"Dadami te dhammapujaya dhira. ","ja441:13.1":"Manim anaggham ruciram pabhassaram, ","ja441:13.2":"Kanthavasattam manibhusitam me; ","ja441:13.3":"Panhassa veyyakaranena tuttho, ","ja441:13.4":"Dadami te dhammapujaya dhira. ","ja441:14.1":"Gavam sahassam usabhanca nagam, ","ja441:14.2":"Ajannayutte ca rathe dasa ime; ","ja441:14.3":"Panhassa veyyakaranena tuttho, ","ja441:14.4":"Dadami te gamavarani solasa”. ","ja441:15.1":"“Sariputto tada nago, ","ja441:15.2":"supanno pana kolito; ","ja441:15.3":"Gandhabbaraja anuruddho, ","ja441:15.4":"raja anandapandito; ","ja441:15.5":"Vidhuro bodhisatto ca, ","ja441:15.6":"evam dharetha jatakan”ti. ","ja441:16.1":"Catuposathiyajatakam tatiyam. "}